    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a new OSPF Router Information (RI) TLV that allows OSPF routers to flood the Seamless Bidirectional Forwarding Detection (S-BFD) Discriminator values associated with a target network identifier.  This mechanism is applicable to both OSPFv2 and OSPFv3.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
